subject: [Good] Mega.co.nz terms have no class action waiver
text:
so many services do have a class action waiver and/or a jury trial waiver, that it becomes notable that this one doesn't. at least i couldn't find any.

Jurisdiction is in New Zealand, btw, and arbitration by the Arbitrators and Mediators Institute of New Zealand Incorporated (AMINZ).
